Invocation Name: sleep rain thunder
des: The sleep rain thunder is a modern insomniac's best friend. Warm and inviting, the sound of rain falls gently on your pillow, soothing you to sleep with calming bass tones of green. The low-power sleep rain thunder has three sound profiles to make sure you have a range of sleep and relaxation.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
